msgctxt "sn19.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The First Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 6. Sattisutta → sattilomasuttaṃ (bj) | satti-māgavi (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn19.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Sattisutta "
msgstr "6. Spear Hairs "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn19.6:1.1"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ sattilomaṃ purisaṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantaṃ. "
msgstr "“Just now, reverend, as I was descending from Vulture’s Peak Mountain I saw a man whose body hairs were spears flying through the air. "

msgctxt "sn19.6:1.2"
msgid "Tassa tā sattiyo uppatitvā uppatitvā tasseva kāye nipatanti. "
msgstr "And those spears kept rising up and falling on his body "

msgctxt "sn19.6:1.3"
msgid "So sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe … "
msgstr "as he screamed in pain. …” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn19.6:1.4"
msgid "eso, bhikkhave, satto imasmiṃyeva rājagahe māgaviko ahosi … pe …. "
msgstr "“That being used to be a deer hunter right here in Rājagaha. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn19.6:1.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

